# flux 3
flux3= file2frame("E:/github/Code_for_publications/GPMM_Glioblastoma/data/PQMM_fluxRxnsMean.txt",row.names = 1)
flux3.annote = file2frame("E:/github/Code_for_publications/GPMM_Glioblastoma/data/Recon3_rxns_v1.txt",row.names = 1)
flux3.annote_org = file2frame("E:/github/Code_for_publications/GPMM_Glioblastoma/data/Recon3_rxns_v1.txt",row.names = 1)


clin = file2frame("E:/github/Code_for_publications/GPMM_Glioblastoma/data/data_bcr_clinical_data_patient_edit.txt")
rownames(clin) = clin$PATIENT_ID
rownames(clin) = gsub('-','.',rownames(clin))
clin$OS_MONTHS = as.numeric(clin$OS_MONTHS)
clin$DFS_MONTHS = as.numeric(clin$DFS_MONTHS)

# expr CPM
rawCounts = file2frame("E:/github/Code_for_publications/GPMM_Glioblastoma/data/TCGA-GBM-Coding-Counts.txt",row.names = 1)
require(edgeR)
dge <- DGEList(counts=as.matrix(rawCounts)) 
keep <- filterByExpr(dge)
dge <- dge[keep,,keep.lib.sizes=FALSE]
dge <- calcNormFactors(dge)
logCPM <- cpm(dge, log=TRUE, prior.count=3)
exprCPM = logCPM

idxx = rowMeans(abs(flux3))> 1e-6
ida = flux3['DM_atp_c_',] > 1e-6
flux3 = flux3[idxx,ida]
flux3.log2= as.matrix(log2(abs(flux3)+1e-6))
list[IA,IB] = ismember(rownames(flux3.log2),rownames(flux3.annote))
flux3.annote = flux3.annote[IB,]
exprCPM = exprCPM[,colnames(flux3)]
clin.forflux = clin[colnames(flux3),]

# IDH1 status
IDH1_status = file2frame('E:/github/Code_for_publications/GPMM_Glioblastoma/data/IDH1_mutation.txt')
bx = unique(IDH1_status$Patient.ID)
list[IA,IB] = ismember(bx,IDH1_status$Patient.ID)
IDH1_status = IDH1_status[IB,]
rownames(IDH1_status) = IDH1_status$Patient.ID
rownames(IDH1_status) = gsub('-','.',rownames(IDH1_status))

clin.forflux$IDH1 = IDH1_status[rownames(clin.forflux),]$IDH1.MUT
clin.forflux$IDH1_stats = IDH1_status[rownames(clin.forflux),]$Altered

clin$IDH1 = IDH1_status[rownames(clin),]$IDH1.MUT
clin$IDH1_stats = IDH1_status[rownames(clin),]$Altered

IA = clin.forflux$IDH1_stats == 0
IA[is.na(IA)] = FALSE
expr.delIDH = exprCPM[,IA]
flux.delIDH = as.matrix(abs(flux3[,IA]))
clin.delIDH = clin.forflux[IA,]

metabo_genes = file2frame('E:/github/Code_for_publications/GPMM_Glioblastoma/data/Recon3D gene.txt')
u_metabo_genes = unique(metabo_genes$Symbol)

# get survival data remove IDH1
IA = clin.forflux$IDH1_stats == 0
IA[is.na(IA)] = FALSE


out.survival_del_idh1_gene = data.frame(rxn = rownames(exprCPM.met[,IA]),stringsAsFactors = F,
                          #rxn_des = flux3.annote$des,
                          meanExpr = rowMeans(exprCPM.met[,IA]),
                        median_up = rep(0,nrow(exprCPM.met[,IA])),
                        median_down = rep(0,nrow(exprCPM.met[,IA])),
                        deta = rep(1,nrow(exprCPM.met[,IA])),      
                        HR = rep(1,nrow(exprCPM.met[,IA])),
                        pval = rep(1,nrow(exprCPM.met[,IA])),
                        fdr = rep(1,nrow(exprCPM.met[,IA])))
for (i in 1:nrow(out.survival_del_idh1_gene)){
    
    cutoff = median(exprCPM.met[i,IA])
    survival_time = clin.forflux[IA,]$OS_MONTHS
    survival_status = clin.forflux[IA,]$OS_STATUS == 'DECEASED'
    st0 = exprCPM.met[i,IA] > cutoff
    st = rep('low flux',length(st0))
    st[st0] = 'high flux'
    out.survival_del_idh1_gene$median_up[i] = median(survival_time[st0],na.rm =T)
    out.survival_del_idh1_gene$median_down[i] = median(survival_time[!st0],na.rm =T)
    out.survival_del_idh1_gene$deta[i] = out.survival_del_idh1_gene$median_up[i] - 
                                    out.survival_del_idh1_gene$median_down[i]
    xx=survdiff(Surv(survival_time,survival_status)~st0)
    out.survival_del_idh1_gene$pval[i] = pchisq(xx$chisq, length(xx$n)-1, lower.tail = FALSE)
    out.survival_del_idh1_gene$HR[i] = (xx$obs[2]/xx$exp[2])/(xx$obs[1]/xx$exp[1])
}
out.survival_del_idh1_gene$fdr = p.adjust(out.survival_del_idh1_gene$pval,method = 'fdr')

# get survival data remove IDH1
IA = clin.forflux$IDH1_stats == 0
IA[is.na(IA)] = FALSE


out.survival_del_idh1 = data.frame(rxn = rownames(flux3.log2[,IA]),stringsAsFactors = F,
                          rxn_des = flux3.annote$des,
                          meanflux = rowMeans(flux3[,IA]),
                        median_up = rep(0,nrow(flux3.log2[,IA])),
                        median_down = rep(0,nrow(flux3.log2[,IA])),
                        deta = rep(1,nrow(flux3.log2[,IA])),      
                        HR = rep(1,nrow(flux3.log2[,IA])),
                        pval = rep(1,nrow(flux3.log2[,IA])),
                        fdr = rep(1,nrow(flux3.log2[,IA])))
for (i in 1:nrow(out.survival_del_idh1)){
    
    cutoff = median(flux3.log2[i,IA])
    survival_time = clin.forflux[IA,]$OS_MONTHS
    survival_status = clin.forflux[IA,]$OS_STATUS == 'DECEASED'
    st0 = flux3.log2[i,IA] > cutoff
    st = rep('low flux',length(st0))
    st[st0] = 'high flux'
    out.survival_del_idh1$median_up[i] = median(survival_time[st0],na.rm =T)
    out.survival_del_idh1$median_down[i] = median(survival_time[!st0],na.rm =T)
    out.survival_del_idh1$deta[i] = out.survival_del_idh1$median_up[i] - 
                                    out.survival_del_idh1$median_down[i]
    xx=survdiff(Surv(survival_time,survival_status)~st0)
    out.survival_del_idh1$pval[i] = pchisq(xx$chisq, length(xx$n)-1, lower.tail = FALSE)
    out.survival_del_idh1$HR[i] = (xx$obs[2]/xx$exp[2])/(xx$obs[1]/xx$exp[1])
}
out.survival_del_idh1$fdr = p.adjust(out.survival_del_idh1$pval,method = 'fdr')
out.survival_del_idh1 = cbind(out.survival_del_idh1,flux3.annote)
survival_del_idh1_forWDA = out.survival_del_idh1
survival_del_idh1_forWDA$`Case - Control.log2FC` = 1-out.survival_del_idh1$HR
survival_del_idh1_forWDA$`Case - Control.PV` = out.survival_del_idh1$pval
survival_del_idh1_forWDA$`Case - Control.log2FC` = out.survival_del_idh1$HR-1

In [15]:
n = nrow(flux3.sigrxns)
n = n*(n-1)/2+100
out.network = data.frame(x1 =rep('a',n),stringsAsFactors = F,
                         x2 = rep('a',n),
                         p = rep(1,n),
                         r = rep(0,n))
k = 1
tnames = rownames(flux3.sigrxns)
for(i in 1:(nrow(flux3.sigrxns)-1)){
    for (j in i:nrow(flux3.sigrxns)){
        tc = cor.test(flux3.sigrxns[i,],flux3.sigrxns[j,])
        out.network$x1[k] = tnames[i]
        out.network$x2[k] = tnames[j]
        out.network$p[k] = tc$p.value
        out.network$r[k] = as.vector(tc$estimate)
        k = k+1
    }
}
writetxt(out.network,'./out/sig_rxns_network_del_idh1_0.01.txt')
idaa = out.network$r > 0.6
writetxt(out.network[idaa,],'./out/sig_rxns_network_del_idh1_0.01_R0.6.txt')
